1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
Did you know the Moon pulls on our oceans?

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:07,200
Its gravity stretches Earth, creating bulges in the water.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:11,200
These bulges mean high tides where the pull is strongest.

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:15,600
But there's another bulge on the opposite side of Earth, too.

5
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:19,200
This creates two high tides each day, every day.

6
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:21,200
Curious about more cosmic wonders?

7
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:22,800
Hit subscribe for more!
